### Key Decision: No CourseType Enum
```python
# ❌ Don't do this
class CourseType(Enum):
    FREE = "FREE"
    PAID = "PAID"

# ✅ Do this
class Course:
    price: float  # 0 = free, >0 = paid
    
    def is_free(self) -> bool:
        return self.price == 0
```

