### Methods
| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `add_question(question)` | Add a question |
| `calculate_score(answers)` | Calculate score from student answers |
| `is_passed(score)` | Returns score >= passing_score |

### Example:
```python
quiz = Quiz(quiz_id=1, title="Variables Quiz", passing_score=70)
quiz.add_question(Question("What is x = 5?", ["Variable", "Function"], 0))

student_answers = {1: 0}  # question_id: selected_option
score = quiz.calculate_score(student_answers)  # 100
passed = quiz.is_passed(score)  # True
```

