## 🧪 Implementation Order

| Step | What | Why |
|------|------|-----|
| 1 | Enums | No dependencies |
| 2 | Question | Simplest class |
| 3 | Quiz | Uses Question |
| 4 | Submodule | Has optional Quiz |
| 5 | Module | Contains Submodules |
| 6 | User | Standalone |
| 7 | Course | Uses Module, User |
| 8 | Enrollment | Links User + Course |
| 9 | Certificate | Uses User + Course |
